@startuml
left to right direction
actor "用户" as User

usecase "创建图形" as CreateGraphic
usecase "选择图形" as SelectGraphic
usecase "删除图形" as DeleteGraphic
usecase "调整图形尺寸" as ResizeGraphic
usecase "移动图形" as MoveGraphic
usecase "创建图层" as CreateLayer
usecase "图层导航" as LayerNavigation
usecase "等比例缩放" as UniformScaling

User --> CreateGraphic
User --> SelectGraphic
User --> DeleteGraphic
User --> ResizeGraphic
User --> MoveGraphic
User --> CreateLayer
User --> LayerNavigation
User --> UniformScaling

' 等比例缩放必须基于选择图形
UniformScaling ..> SelectGraphic : include

' 按住Shift时调整图形尺寸扩展为等比例缩放
ResizeGraphic ..> UniformScaling : extend
@enduml
